@startuml
actor Client

participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Eureka Server" as EU
participant "Credit Controller" as CC
participant "Credit Service (RxJava)" as CS
participant "Mongo Reactive Repository" as REPO

Client -> GW: POST /api/credits
GW -> EU: Resolve CREDIT-SERVICE
EU --> GW: service instance

GW -> CC: forward request

CC -> CS: create(credit)
CS -> REPO: save(credit)

REPO --> CS: Mono<Credit>
CS --> CC: Single<Credit>

CC --> GW: HTTP 201
GW --> Client: Response JSON
@enduml